HEADWORD: Scranch
<hw>Scranch</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p.
p.</pos> <conjf>Scranched</conjf> <pr>(?)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
